e:T6e4,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Alli AI better than Serpstat?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Alli AI scores 7.0 overall while Serpstat scores 7.0. Alli AI is best for agencies and multi-site management, while Serpstat excels for SMBs and in-house SEOs."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Alli AI or Serpstat?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Alli AI starts at $299/mo and Serpstat starts at $69/mo.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Alli AI to Serpstat?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Alli AI and Serpstat support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Alli AI vs Serpstat?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Alli AI holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Serpstat has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 6/10. Users praise Alli AI for automatically implements seo changes and Serpstat for good value for comprehensive features."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Alli AI or Serpstat?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Serpstat for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Alli AI remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize automatically implements seo changes. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}5:[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$e"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"compare-header","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","h1",null,{"childr